nl.tue.geometrycore.graphs.simple

Class SimpleGraph<TGeom extends OrientedGeometry<TGeom>,TVertex extends SimpleVertex<TGeom,TVertex,TEdge>,TEdge extends SimpleEdge<TGeom,TVertex,TEdge>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tue.geometrycore.graphs.simple.SimpleGraph<TGeom,TVertex,TEdge>
  • Type Parameters:
    TGeom - The geometry of an edge, must inherit from OrientedGeometry
    TVertex - The class of a vertex
    TEdge - The class of an edge

    public abstract class SimpleGraph<TGeom extends OrientedGeometry<TGeom>,TVertex extends SimpleVertex<TGeom,TVertex,TEdge>,TEdge extends SimpleEdge<TGeom,TVertex,TEdge>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to represent an undirected graph with a simple edge-list implementation. It provides standard graph functionality, but is abstract to allow for easy addition of auxiliary data to its elements. For practical use, create derivations of SimpleGraph, SimpleEdge and SimpleVertex.
